com.datastax.driver.core

Class ServerSideTimestampGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastax.driver.core.ServerSideTimestampGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimestampGenerator

    public class ServerSideTimestampGenerator
extends Object
implements TimestampGenerator
    A timestamp generator that always returns Long.MIN_VALUE, in order to let Cassandra assign server-side timestamps.
